The Commander-in-Chief of Defence Services (Burmese language: တပ်မတော်ကာကွယ်ရေးဦးစီးချုပ်) is the commanding officer of the Tatmadaw (Burmese language: တပ်မတော်), the armed forces of Myanmar.
